Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So go outside and eat the\N weeds growing in our lawn.}{Đi ra ngoài ăn cỏ trong vườn đi.}Ra ngoài ăn đi, còn cỏ trong vườn đó~
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{That's not food!}Ăn có được đâu!!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Then go buy some seaweed.}Thế tự mua tảo biển đi.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It's good for baldness.}Tốt cho người hói đấy.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm not going bald!}Anh mày không có hói nhé!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm not, right?}Tao không có hói, đúng không?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Right?}Đúng không mày?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, is this going somewhere?}Nè, nói chuyện gì liên quan thế cha nội?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.75,0:15:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What I'm saying is you've got\N it good! You just don't know it!}Đã nói là những gì tao nói mày đã nghe hết chưa! Mày thậm chí còn không hiểu nữa!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Wait, don't tell me...}Đừng nói là... chú mày...!!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.49,0:15:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, {we're having curry today.}hôm nay mình sẽ ăn cà ri đó.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure if it's good enough.}Không biết em làm có ngon không nữa.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Welcome back}Mừng em về nhà, Yuu-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.48,0:15:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Will you have dinner? A bath?}Em muốn ăn tối? Hay là đi tắm?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.21,0:15:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Or do you want to have}Hay là em muốn xơi {\i1}{me}chị{\i0} {first?}trước?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.17,0:15:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{And she does that every day,\N wearing a Naked Apron!}Và chị ấy như thế mỗi ngày, mặc một cái Tạp Dề thôi!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.66,0:15:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Keep dreaming.}Mơ à chú?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{And what the hell is a “Naked Apron”?}Mà cái "Tạp Dề Khỏa Thân" là sao hả?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.98,0:15:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Don't you know? It's where a girl\N wears nothing but an apron}Mày không biết sao? Đó chính là cô gái nude với tạp dề thôi{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yow...}Đau...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Where are you headed?}Mày đi đâu thế?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to peek in.}Đi nhìn thử xem ấy mà.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ah}A, Yuuya-oniichan!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Oh, right. Just getting a drink.}Oh, a, chỉ là đi kiếm nước uống thôi.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Sure, wait here! I'll get you something.}Em hiểu rồi, anh đợi chút nhé! Em sẽ đi lấy cho anh.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ảnh đang nhìn, đanh nhìn đó!{He's watching!}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He looks really weirded out to me.}Sao thấy mình dị hợm thế nào ấy...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But you were the one who bought this apron}Nhưng cậu là người mua cái tạp dề này mà, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.73,0:16:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I thought it looked cute back at the shop.}Tớ cứ nghĩ nó dễ thương khi nhìn ở cửa hàng thôi.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{If you'd like, why don't you take a bath first.}Nếu em muốn thì đi tắm trước đi.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It's going to take us a little while longer.}Vẫn còn 1 lúc nữa mới xong mà.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.10,0:16:18.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Isn't that what a wife tells her husband?!}Chờ đã! {Đó không phải là câu mà người vợ nên nói cho chồng ư?!}Đó là câu "vợ nói chồng nghe" mà?!!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.55,0:16:21.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{She thinks she's married to him?}Mụ nghĩ sẽ được làm vợ ảnh sao?!!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I already drew a bath, so it's all ready for you.}Chị đã tắm rồi nên em cứ thoải mái đi.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Now look here!}Chờ đã, cô đấy...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{God!}Mồ!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Give it a rest}Bỏ đi mà, Hiyori!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Um...}Etou...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{She's right!}Chị ấy đúng đó!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You're only getting in our way,\N so why don't you take that bath?}Anh chỉ chắn đường tụi em thôi, nên anh đi tắm tốt hơn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but Torii's here too. I'll take one later.}Uh, nhưng mà Torii ở đây mà. Có lẽ anh sẽ tắm sau.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if Yuu-kun came get some appetizers.}Yuu-kun tính xuống ăn vụng món khai vị hay sao ấy nhỉ.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It looked like he was only getting a drink.}Có lẽ anh ấy chỉ đi lấy nước uống thôi.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.85,0:16:56.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{I wondered how they were getting along, but it looks fine from here.}Sợ họ không thể hòa thuận, nhưng nhìn vậy cũng an tâm rồi.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Maybe I will take that bath.}Có lẽ mình nên đi tắm thôi....
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.94,0:17:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukina-san... {that's amazing.}chị giỏi thật đó.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What is?}Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You're handling everything all at once.}Chị làm được tất cả mọi việc.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You know your way around the kitchen, just like a pro.}Thuần thục từ đầu đến cuối, cứ như dân chuyên nghiệp ấy.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm not that good. I'm just used to doing this.}Chị không giỏi thế đâu. Chỉ là làm quá quen thôi.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You are?}Quen ạ?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.20,0:17:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I used to be a latchkey kid. I had to make food for myself.}Chị từng sống một mình nên phải tự làm thức ăn cho mình.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What about you?}Mitsuki-chan thì sao?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.99,0:17:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Before my mom remarried, I used to eat ready-\Nmade meals whenever she came home late.}Trước khi mẹ em tái hôn, em luôn là người chuẩn bị thức ăn.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So I've only begun learning how to cook.}Vì thế nên em đã học cách nấu ăn.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But I still have a lot to learn.}Nhưng em vẫn còn phải học rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Thế à.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{when I started making my own lunch, I found out that I like doing it.}khi em bắt đầu tự làm bữa ăn cho mình thì em thấy thích thú điều đó.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.07,0:18:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I knew it! You were making Yuu-kun's lunches!}Biết ngay mà! Em đã làm bữa trưa cho Yuu-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.62,0:18:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{We take turns only because it's unfair otherwise!}Tụi em chỉ thay phiên nhau làm cho công bằng thôi ạ!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So I stuck nose where it didn't belong.}Vậy ra chị là kì đà cản mũi rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-kun {could have said something.}cũng không chịu nói gì hết.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You didn't do anything wrong!}Chị không làm gì sai cả!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He ate everything in your bentou.}Anh ấy ăn hết mọi thứ trong hộp bentou của Yuukina-san mà.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.05,0:18:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But he hardly even touched... my lunch.}Nhưng anh ấy lại hầu như... không hề đụng đến hộp bentou của em.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You're overreacting!}Em phản ứng thái quá rồi!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.30,0:18:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It's only because he was full, I'm sure of it!}Chỉ vì anh ấy no thôi, chị chắc chắn là thế!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.32,0:18:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You're so adorable, Mitsuki-chan!\N You don't even try to hide it!}Em dễ thương thật đó, Mitsuki-chan!\N Lại còn thật thà nữa!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Hey}Nè, Yukina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.79,form,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur0.5\fs25\3c&HA59E89&\c&HA59E89&\b\pos(342,387.667)\frx0\fry358\frz0.2526\fscx75\fscy61}Phá{\3c&H9D9169&\c&H9D9169&}p
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.79,form,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.5\fs25\3c&HA59E89&\c&HE8E8DB&\b\pos(342,387.667)\frx0\fry358\frz0.2526\fscx75\fscy61}Phá{\3c&H9D9169&}p
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.79,notes,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\bord0\fr1\fs13\pos(345,375.333)}Gia vị
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Actually, Yuu-kun was talking about you.}Này nhé, Yuu-kun đã nói về em đó
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.56,0:18:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He said you were now making food for him.}Em ấy nói dạo này Mitsuki-chan đã bắt đầu làm thức ăn cho em ấy.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{And it made him blush.}Điều đó làm em ấy bất ngờ đó.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.76,0:18:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-kun {had to do everything around the \Nhouse since his dad was so busy with work.}{phải làm tất cả mọi việc trong nhà khi bố phải bận bịu với công việc.} đấy,, luôn phải làm mọi việc khi bố bận.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.97,0:19:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I think he's glad you're making meals for him.}Chị nghĩ em ấy mừng vì em đã làm bữa trưa đấy.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It won't matter how it tastes.}Ngon hay dở cũng không quan trọng đâu.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{Is that true?}Thật vậy ư?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.09,0:19:14.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{Does}Liệu {\i0}{this}thứ này{\i1} {actually make him sort of happy?}có thật sự làm anh ấy vui không?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What are you saying?}Cậu đang nói gì thế?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{If it doesn't taste good, he won't eat it!}Nếu nó không ngon thì sao anh ấy lại phải ăn nó!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! This is none of your business!}Im đi! Đâu phải chuyện của cậu!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.09,0:19:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But if Onii-chan's happy anyway, then it's all good!}Nhưng mà nếu Onii-chan vui thì cũng tốt nhỉ!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{All we have to do is make something\N so tasty he'll eat every bite!}Chúng ta phải làm cái gì đó thật ngon\N để anh ấy ăn sạch luôn!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Nè!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You'll see}Rồi anh sẽ thấy, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yes! That's the spirit!}Đúng thế! Tinh thần phải thế chứ!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Being a good cook takes practice.}Nấu càng nhiều thì tay nghề càng lên mà.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Đau quá...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.26,0:19:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Sorry}Xin lỗi nhé, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I don't believe this!}Không thể tin được!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.62,0:20:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Why did she leave that thing open?!}Sao cô ta lại không đóng nắp chai gia vị đó chứ?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.54,0:20:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukina-san {didn't do it on purpose.}đâu có cố ý đâu.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What? Are you starting to}Gì cơ? Cậu bắt đầu {\i1}{accept}chấp nhận{\i0} {Miss Funbags?}Con mụ ngực bự đó ư?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Then that means she has the advantage.}Cứ thế này thì tình thế nghiêng về cô ta mất.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Fine, I'll just take it up a notch,}Được rồi, tới lúc giở chiêu rồi,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{and seduce him wearing this!}và ép anh ta phải mang thứ này!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Hey! You idiot!}Dừng lại đi, đồ ngốc!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I can't walk out of here in}Làm sao tớ có thể ra ngoài trong bộ dạng {\i1}{this!}này{\i0} chứ!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Now I get it!}Ra là như thế!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So}Thì ra {\i1}{that's}cái này{\i0} là {the Naked Apron!}Tạp Dề Khỏa Thân!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What?}Sao vậy chứ?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.86,0:20:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{She threw away the lunch she made?}Em ấy vứt hết bữa trưa em ấy làm ư?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.37,0:20:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I was too full at lunch, so I was\N saving it for later tonight.}Em ăn hơi quá nên tính dành cho bữa tối mà.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.93,0:21:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Okay, so that's why she was so moody.}Thì ra vì thế em ấy lại ủ rũ như thế.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So what's with the swollen cheek?}Thế sao má mày sưng lên thế?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.46,0:21:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Nothing to worry about.}Không có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.89,0:21:13.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{I don't think that slap ruined their chances.}Sưng cỡ đó thì sao mà "không có gì" được...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Wait, don't tell me...}Đ-Đừng nói là...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.47,0:21:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Geez, that again? Lay off.}Lại nữa à? Dẹp dùm đê.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.11,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{overlap}Mitsuki-chan {slapped you}tát mày
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.36,0:21:23.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{But from the looks of it, they're far from being in love—I think.}Nhưng khi nhìn từ đây, họ còn xa vời với tình yêu lắm.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.40,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{overlap}{because you caught her wearing a Naked Apron}bởi vì mày bắt gặp em ấy mặc Tạp Dề Khỏa Thân
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.32,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{after getting out of the tub!}sau khi ra khỏi bồn tắm chứ gì!
